 <span data-ttu-id="abe43-114">O <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> construtor inicializa o <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A> propriedade.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="abe43-114">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor initializes the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="abe43-115">O identificador deve ser exclusivo dentro de uma determinado gramática.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="abe43-115">The identifier must be unique within a given grammar.</span></span>  

