## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="abe43-156">O exemplo a seguir cria uma gramática que reconhece a frase "é de um país que ganhou o Cup World" seguido do nome de um país que ganhou o Cup do mundo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="abe43-156">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="abe43-157">Depois de criar o <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> objeto `winnerRule` e fornecê-lo o identificador de cadeia de caracteres `WorldCupWinner`, o exemplo usa o <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> método acrescentar a cadeia de caracteres "é um país que ganhou o Cup World" para a regra.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="abe43-157">After creating the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object `winnerRule` and giving it the string identifier `WorldCupWinner`, the example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> method to append the string  "A nation that has won the World Cup is" to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="abe43-158">O exemplo cria duas regras adicionais, `ruleEurope` e `ruleSAmerica`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="abe43-158">The example then creates two additional rules, `ruleEurope` and  `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="abe43-159">Novamente usando o <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> método, o exemplo anexa um <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> o objeto para o `WorldCupWinner` regra que contém referências de regra a `ruleEurope` e `ruleSAmerica`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="abe43-159">Again using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> method, the example appends an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object to the `WorldCupWinner` rule that contains rule references to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span>  

```csharp  
// Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
// and set its scope to public.  
SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  

// Add the introduction.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  

// Create the rule for the European nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  

// Create the rule for the South American nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  

// Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  

// Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
// the root rule of the document.  
document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
document.Root = winnerRule;  
```



## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="abe43-186">O valor padrão para o escopo é `Private`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="abe43-186">The default value for scope is `Private`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="abe43-187">Uma regra privada só poderá ser ativada para o reconhecimento por uma referência de regra da regra na gramática seu recipiente raiz ou de outra regra que é referenciada da regra raiz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="abe43-187">A private rule can only be activated for recognition by a rule reference from the root rule in its containing grammar or from another rule that is referenced from the root rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="abe43-188">Uma regra privada não pode ser referenciada por uma gramática externa, a menos que a regra privada é declarada como a regra raiz de seu recipiente gramática.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="abe43-188">A private rule cannot be referenced by an external grammar, unless the private rule is declared as the root rule of its containing grammar.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="abe43-189">Se seu escopo é definido como `Public`, uma <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> objeto pode ser ativado para o reconhecimento por uma referência de um <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> objeto na gramática do recipiente ou de uma regra em uma gramática externa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="abe43-189">If its scope is set to `Public`, an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object can be activated for recognition by a reference from a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> object in the containing grammar or from a rule in an external grammar.</span></span>  



